{"tid":1905712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無戴口罩同搭升降機　女子與患者共處1分鐘全程沒交談即中招","createTime":"2020-03-01T12:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T05:54:52.000Z","uid":132380,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2fa6da81bc51593211a75440bcdf7bf1ed197cf8","tid":1905712,"uid":132380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:25:51.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎（武漢肺炎）疫情擴散全球，其中南韓的確診病例已至少達到3150宗，死亡人數增至17人。當中，一名女公務員與後來確診的患者在升降機內共處約一分鐘，雙方全程沒交談，只因未戴口罩，最後亦被確診感染新冠肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">據韓媒JTBC報道，南韓首爾城東區工作的一名41歲女公務員，上月18日與一名後來確診的明成教會牧師共乘同一部升降機。其間兩人並無沒有交談，但均沒有戴上口罩，兩人在升降機內共處了約1分鐘，該名女公務員之後確診。不過，當時升降機內還有女公務員的兩名孩子，但由於兩名孩子當時均有戴口罩，經檢測證實他們對病毒呈陰性反應。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大韓醫學會主席崔在旭（Chae-Wook Choi）指出，電梯內是狹窄空間，很難保持超過2米的安全距離，可能還是會透過微小的飛沫侵入肺部，也可能是碰觸到按鈕上殘留的病毒而感染。江北三星病院教授仔表示：「就算只是短時間，在密切接觸的電梯裡，一定要戴口罩。離開電梯以後，也要洗手30秒以上。」"},{"pid":"9adaa1588cad1c70144faa4f6b6c8add58f4ceea","tid":1905712,"uid":73959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T13:06:38.000Z","msg":"係咪個老母掂完𨋢制唔洗手咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a922994ac4a16ec8b796e9844d3c5231c419eb","tid":1905712,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:42:43.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"d3cdf98542a3c4b329fe64faf8a2bdea4b6a2f5a","tid":1905712,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:46:15.000Z","msg":"香港有邊度係唔駛搭lift，所以叫人唔駛戴口罩都靠害"},{"pid":"80253cf7901e750ef6e1396b9f4bbd7b5b3efa92","tid":1905712,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"WHO 同CDC 仲叫人健康就唔洗戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9ebd3bc03ef539905cc38515d6e75582f33167","tid":1905712,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:50:48.000Z","msg":"個帶毒者做過咩先？ <br />\n可能佢捽完眼， 㩒lift呢"},{"pid":"136e4aa5aeb4fb1f001dd929cf4088a828470710","tid":1905712,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:50:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static5.orstatic.com/userphoto/photo/1/1C5/009IDK488EDDC9F70B5BF3px.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic5.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto%2Fphoto%2F1%2F1C5%2F009IDK488EDDC9F70B5BF3px.jpg&h=9209fd55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以前既肺癆係肺結核細菌會易d 消滅(用傳統消毒方法)<br />\n<br />\n而武漢肺炎<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>病毒因有表面外層保護</strong></span><br />\n所以難以消滅<br />\n<br />\n其實同以前既肺癆差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n方法係注重個人衛生, 每個人自己戴口罩/豬嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經可以大大減低傳播性"},{"pid":"ac64128d2b7d22bf27f2be58982f0990d8676c48","tid":1905712,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:51:14.000Z","msg":"老師又中"},{"pid":"141c9dadb9176a904d82fb1c62bcb16474d8534a","tid":1905712,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:51:31.000Z","msg":"之前鄰國都有單街市15秒啦"},{"pid":"e7353a0374d96aa6b94af9974b776d13313cb87f","tid":1905712,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:50:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"></span>"},{"pid":"5516de8a240981d7bdb820842b6967841813e26d","tid":1905712,"uid":220779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80253cf7901e750ef6e1396b9f4bbd7b5b3efa92","tid":1905712,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"WHO 同CDC 仲叫人健康就唔洗戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:52:27.000Z","msg":"你點知係接觸傳播 例如摸lift制<br />\n定係因為係搭lift期間無戴飛沫傳播<br />\nCDC有開到聲要勤洗手"},{"pid":"d7960c105cd6ab91fcdc22e36bf3d0b038ea9391","tid":1905712,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:53:49.000Z","msg":"會空氣傳播就搵國家認左佢啦"},{"pid":"1c123a9cdfb7c75355be562347f5de33a4882cdd","tid":1905712,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:54:52.000Z","msg":"因為呼吸呼出嚟 d 空氣有病毒, 隔離一吸咪中招"}]}